'''Baka rock''' was a type of [[Music/Legends|music]] invented by [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]]. Apart from Gamorrean expatriate communities, the genre mostly failed to find a significant appreciative audience across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]],<ref name="blog">{{SW|url=news/slugthrowers-an-overview-of-popular-music-and-musicians-in-a-galaxy-far-far-away-part-1|series=Slugthrowers: An Overview of Popular Music and Musicians in a Galaxy Far, Far Away|text=Part 1|nolive=1}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Baka rock can be heard in ''[[LEGO Star Wars II: The Original Trilogy]]'' as well as ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Complete Saga]]''.

